{"tid":1066871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港媽抱小孩搭長途巴　婦人拒讓座　網民狂轟","createTime":"2019-03-18T07:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T09:59:28.000Z","uid":225464,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"336c96c62de70aa7d8da2365a002558e19e07702","tid":1066871,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>港媽抱小孩搭長途巴 婦人拒讓座 網民狂轟</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TRKnyG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TRKnyG&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4MzQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=90eb402f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TRKnyG</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190318/photo/bkn-20190318124657011-0318_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190318150755\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190318124657011-0318_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190318150755&h=e7ae6e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁行李架要嚟做咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖則關愛座有需要就可以坐，但行李都有坐的權利？近日有大媽霸佔關愛座，更用來擺放行李，惹怒一眾網民。<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「香港交通突發報料區」的貼文指，有媽媽抱着1歲小孩乘坐機場巴士前往元朗，惟車廂已滿座，欲尋找關愛座。<br />\n<br />\n據網民所述，有中年女子卻強佔座位，坐在近走道的位置，更把大包小包的隨身物品放在靠窗的空位上，堅拒讓座︰「你哋搵其他位坐啦！呢個位我要放我嘅行李！」<br />\n<br />\n發貼者怒斥︰「原來行李唔擺行李架，係要畀位佢坐㗎！真係今日先見識到超級無敵無恥之徒！」<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛建議︰「可要求車長協助，車長有權處理」、「叫司機來叫她入多一次車資」。有人表示認出該女子︰「呢個女人，唔係第一次了」、「上次同佢搭埋一部巴士，佢坐出面，裏面有個位，跟住有人想坐入去，佢竟然話入面個位有人坐」。"},{"pid":"cae1b8c9af89e54d9659e6547d34085638f34c8d","tid":1066871,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗"},{"pid":"e9ab24a1fff0847ad7c11081eedc6d0817a30818","tid":1066871,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cae1b8c9af89e54d9659e6547d34085638f34c8d","tid":1066871,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae62ac58daceea9c829f8dbc31e06b85443b197b","tid":1066871,"uid":66099,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"香港人三等公民，學乜人要坐"},{"pid":"485dd9a5f38bdd8348f597f01045c556dca6b014","tid":1066871,"uid":14715,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"直接坐落去咪撚理佢"},{"pid":"2bc11fab8f8c8aebd88ca8f4c37d966bc22a24d3","tid":1066871,"uid":207706,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"打乜撚嘢格啊   呢啲垃圾開佢樣啦"},{"pid":"bb762cdc2aa670c7020af53d738653ff460ba2fd","tid":1066871,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"咁樣又真係仆街wo"},{"pid":"eb7eafb1ad1feb4db63968f06cca8118605a8231","tid":1066871,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"叫司機停車處理"},{"pid":"7584dcf1aac51a90cd0a7e1ee06172c9fb58f8d4","tid":1066871,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"霸左都要讓比你<br />\n咁霸來做乜<br />\n陀仔出街又要人老奉讓, 惡過碼頭姑哩"},{"pid":"0928f1eaa603ef9ddad948cf0ac0141aa0712edf","tid":1066871,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"苞蓉"},{"pid":"7025e7a5f6804d1468ca99445668a3b4bf52b4a1","tid":1066871,"uid":31371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7584dcf1aac51a90cd0a7e1ee06172c9fb58f8d4","tid":1066871,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"霸左都要讓比你<br />\n咁霸來做乜<br />\n陀仔出街又要人老奉讓, 惡過碼頭姑哩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d22186294e2b821be2f88261987dbdf36142bf","tid":1066871,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"一睇就知廟街企街嗰啲北菇嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=